<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>초기 설정</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding: 36px 40px; width: 100%; max-width: 560px; }
    h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1f36; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 12px; }
    .result-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .result-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; }
    .result-item.ok  { background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0; color: #065f46; }
    .result-item.err { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; color: #991b1b; }
    .result-icon { font-size: 15px; margin-top: 1px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .section { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .kv { display: flex; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .kv .k { color: #6b7280; min-width: 60px; }
    .kv .v { font-weight: 700; color: #1a1f36; }
    .warn { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 11px 28px; background: #1a1f36; color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn:hover { background: #2d3561; }
    .btn-retry { background: #dc2626; }
    .btn-retry:hover { background: #b91c1c; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <h1>시스템 초기 설정</h1>

  <div class="result-list">
    <% results.forEach(function(r) { %>
      <div class="result-item <%= r.ok ? 'ok' : 'err' %>">
        <span class="result-icon"><%= r.ok ? '✅' : '❌' %></span>
        <span><%= r.msg %></span>
      </div>
    <% }); %>
  </div>

  <% if (!hasError) { %>
    <div class="section">
      <h3>기본 관리자 계정</h3>
      <div class="kv"><span class="k">사번</span><span class="v">0000</span></div>
      <div class="kv"><span class="k">비밀번호</span><span class="v">0000</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="warn">
      ⚠️ 보안을 위해 로그인 후 <strong>즉시 비밀번호를 변경</strong>하십시오.
    </div>

    <a class="btn" href="/login">로그인 페이지로 이동</a>
  <% } else { %>
    <div class="warn">
      ⚠️ 오류가 발생했습니다. <strong>config/db.js</strong> 및 <strong>config/mpoms_db.js</strong>의 DB 접속 정보를 확인하세요.
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-retry" href="/setup">다시 시도</a>
  <% } %>
</div>
</body>
</html>
